    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cato the Cat是一款休闲比赛3游戏，您必须照顾好您的宠物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/1caf9860c66687541b07eb51a892968c.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/1caf9860c66687541b07eb51a892968c.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/1caf9860c66687541b07eb51a892968c.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你必须照顾Cato，一只非常聪明的猫，通过一个三消机制，不要让他逃脱，为此你将不得不喂养他，平息他的种子，给他很多爱和乐趣。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>怎么玩？</strong></h2><strong>选择一块, 您可以使用空格键旋转棋子并将其放置在板上。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b4a9dcca32a64be6ffa7a74b3f15aecc.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b4a9dcca32a64be6ffa7a74b3f15aecc.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b4a9dcca32a64be6ffa7a74b3f15aecc.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>组合 3 件或</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b6acaeb80cc0f8c56a94edbcc15bcfeb.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b6acaeb80cc0f8c56a94edbcc15bcfeb.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b6acaeb80cc0f8c56a94edbcc15bcfeb.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>或水平方向上更多相同类型</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/be1a1b7df9a08e92c870db2e8fa9e8dc.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/be1a1b7df9a08e92c870db2e8fa9e8dc.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/be1a1b7df9a08e92c870db2e8fa9e8dc.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>或垂直.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/ed5af5b915ccc57c853427b1db150a18.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/ed5af5b915ccc57c853427b1db150a18.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/ed5af5b915ccc57c853427b1db150a18.mp4?t=1681